Package movie

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LMovie
    Singleton movie class holding currently loaded movie and its parameters
    MovieCanvas
    Customised canvas for rendering the movie frames and drawing ROIs/metadata
    MovieLoader
    Listener for initiating movie loading and unloading of previous data
    MovieLoaderThread
    Single thread for frame and metadata extraction from a selected movie file
    ROI
    Region of Interest object, allows for setting, modifying, and performing signal processing
    ROICollection
    Singleton ROI collector, managing multiple ROIs
